Terry Matthews

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Sir Terry Matthews
KBE, FREng, FIEE


Born
Terence Hedley Matthews
(1943-06-06) 6 June 1943 (age 74)
Newport, Wales, UK


Residence
Ottawa, Ontario, Canada


Citizenship
Canadian, British


