Since 1970, Matthews has been the premier manufacturer of high quality, specialized hardware for the film, television, still photographic and theatrical industries.Their commitment to the industry continues with imaginative new products, increased focus on customer service and attention to the precise needs of the grip industry. As they venture into the years ahead their pledge is to provide the finest product, service and competitive pricing available in the industry.From stands, hardware, booms, truss and lighting, bags, boxes, camera support, dollies and tracks, to textiles and more, Mathews Studio Equipment provides the finest products. Markertek is your source for Mathews Studio Equipment.Markertek is an authorized dealer for the entire Matthews Studio Equipment line. If you don't see what you're looking for, contact us and we'll do our best to get it for you.
 







